title: Barth gets a tryout with Tampa Bay Tuesday
text:
Barth gets a tryout with Tampa Bay Tuesday Posted: Connor Barth gets another look from Tampa Bay this week. (Source: WECT) WILMINGTON, NC (WECT) - 
A day after tweeting that he was "available" for any interested NFL teams, Connor Barth from Wilmington is getting another shot for a spot with the Tampa Bay Buccaneers. I'm just saying I am available for the right price????... #freeagent @nfl â€” Connor Barth (@contbarth) October 4, 2015 
Barth will try out with his former team Tuesday. Barth has been out of the league this season after Tampa cut him late in training camp. He has also kicked for the Denver Broncos. 
Tampa Bay released rookie kicker Kyle Brindza Monday after a rough Sunday, in which he missed a couple field goals and an extra point. After one of those missed field goals Sunday, Barth took to Twitter to write "I'm just saying I am available for the right price. #free agent"
